@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/v1
@token = SEU_BEARER_TOKEN

### Lista gateways disponiveis
GET {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos/providers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cria pagamento avulso (OpenPix)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openpix",
  "amount": 1500,
  "description": "Pagamento avulso de teste",
  "idempotencyKey": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "customer": {
    "nome": "Bob",
    "email": "bob@openpix.com.br",
    "documento": "47173708052",
    "telefone": "5511940468888"
  },
  "metadata": {
    "origem": "teste-local",
    "pedido": "PED-123"
  }
}

### Lista historico de pagamentos avulsos
GET {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lista pendentes (independente de gateway)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos/pendentes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lista por status
GET {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Busca pagamento por id
GET {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sincroniza status com gateway
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos/1/sincronizar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancela pagamento
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos/1/cancelar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "motivo": "Cancelado pelo operador"
}

### Marca como pago manualmente
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos/1/marcar-pago
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Consulta status direto no gateway
GET {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos/gateway/openpix/SEU_EXTERNAL_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Webhook OpenPix (publico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pagamentos-avulsos/webhook/openpix
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "OPENPIX:CHARGE_COMPLETED",
  "charge": {
    "identifier": "SEU_EXTERNAL_ID",
    "status": "COMPLETED"
  }
}
